Output demo/json.gif

Require ppp

Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 800
Set Height 450
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Type `echo '{"name":"Alice","active":true,"age":30,"address":{"city":"NYC","zip":"10001"},"roles":["admin","user"]}' | ppp`
Enter
Sleep 3s

Sleep 1s
